📚 HOW TO BUY ON POLONIEX 📚

When you add a new "Buy Order" - click on "limit" and change it to "market" price section (Number 1), to set your buying price. This ensures you are buying at market price, so your order is more likely to go through. Then set your buying amount (Number 2) and click on "Buy" (Number 3)

📚 HOW TO SELL ON POLONIEX 📚

When you add a new "Sell Order" - click on "market" and change it to "limit" (Number 1), then click the top LEFT price section, circled in white, to set your selling price (Number 2). This ensures you are selling above market price and gain profits. Then click on "Sell" (Number 3).
